snippet.title: Unholy - TGS announcement trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
Where is Gabriel? Watch the announcement trailer to cross the door between your everyday reality and a dark unholy world to unveil the mystery. Duality Games new psychological horror game mixes exploration, puzzle solving and Stealth action. Brand new indie publisher HOOK will bring it to you on PS5 in 2023.
